msgid ""
"See the [[!wikipedia Linux_malware desc=\"Wikipedia page on Linux "
"malware\"]] for further details."
msgstr ""
"Vedere la [[!wikipedia Linux_malware desc=\"Wikipedia page on Linux "
"malware\"]] per ulteriori dettagli."

